1
00:00:16,640 --> 00:00:17,839
This is Jiaohai News.

2
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:19,039
I'm reporter Xia Wen.

3
00:00:19,239 --> 00:00:20,320
Min Ge, everything's settled.

4
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:21,000
He threw a Molotov cocktail

5
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:22,719
into a residential courtyard.

6
00:00:22,920 --> 00:00:23,679
Police have confirmed

7
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:24,719
the man did it intentionally.

8
00:00:24,719 --> 00:00:26,000
Relax, don't be so tense, Min Ge.

9
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:27,399
My family runs this guesthouse.

10
00:00:27,519 --> 00:00:28,440
It's perfectly safe.

11
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:31,719
Do I look like I'm afraid of the cops?

12
00:00:33,079 --> 00:00:34,399
It's mainly Mao Ge.

13
00:00:34,719 --> 00:00:36,359
Huang Qiuping, and whoever's behind Mao Ge,

14
00:00:37,479 --> 00:00:38,880
they probably know we're turning on them.

15
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:41,119
Luo Xiao.

16
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:43,240
How dare he scheme against me.

17
00:00:44,799 --> 00:00:46,240
This isn't over between us.

18
00:00:57,039 --> 00:00:57,799
Coming.

19
00:00:59,320 --> 00:00:59,960
Old Chen.

20
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:01,280
Nice catch today.

21
00:01:01,439 --> 00:01:03,439
Of course. Hook drops, fish bites.

22
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:11,519
Now remember,

23
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,719
don't throw out the bladder or guts.

24
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:13,799
Pack them all up for me.

25
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:15,560
Sure, I was going to pack them anyway.

26
00:01:19,239 --> 00:01:20,519
Here, all done.

27
00:01:20,719 --> 00:01:21,439
That fast?

28
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,519
I'll make fish offal soup when we get back.

29
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:31,959
Boss.

30
00:01:32,480 --> 00:01:33,280
What is this?

31
00:01:33,799 --> 00:01:34,760
What else could it be?

32
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,040
Fish intestines.

33
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,599
Fish intestines? Come take a look.

34
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,000
Doesn't it look like...

35
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:45,200
a fingernail?

36
00:01:55,719 --> 00:01:56,560
Mao Ge.

37
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,239
Is he dead?

38
00:02:01,879 --> 00:02:02,680
Huang Qiuping.

39
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,400
You must be joking.

40
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:14,120
What do you think Mao Ge and I are?

41
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:16,439
Each doing our own thing?

42
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:19,520
Bailing on each other when trouble hits?

43
00:02:23,199 --> 00:02:24,840
That's what you all think, isn't it?

44
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,280
That's why

45
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,639
you dared try to fool me with this.

46
00:02:33,599 --> 00:02:34,520
Mr. Big-shot Lawyer.

47
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,840
You may be well-informed,

48
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,479
but you've never seen it.

49
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,879
When a knife was pointed right at my chest,

50
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:43,280
Mao Ge took the blade for me.

51
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:45,360
The ten years he did time,

52
00:02:45,919 --> 00:02:47,599
I was the one who held down the fort.

53
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,639
I welcomed him back when he got out.

54
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,159
The things the two of us have been through

55
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:54,159
are ten thousand times dirtier and uglier

56
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:56,159
than anything you could ever imagine.

57
00:02:56,919 --> 00:02:57,719
So...

58
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,639
divorce?

59
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:03,000
Where is he?

60
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,919
Where is he?

61
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:14,280
He's dead.

62
00:03:20,199 --> 00:03:22,280
He threatened me with my child,

63
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:25,360
made me help him flee.

64
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:28,680
He climbed into my trunk.

65
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,039
I...

66
00:03:30,919 --> 00:03:32,080
But the lock broke.

67
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:33,719
It was too hot.

68
00:03:33,759 --> 00:03:35,159
He suffocated in the trunk.

69
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:37,879
Huang Qiuping,

70
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,080
I really had no choice.

71
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,879
My child is only eight,

72
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,479
and she's sick.

73
00:03:43,919 --> 00:03:44,680
She can't...

74
00:03:45,479 --> 00:03:47,000
She can't... can't be without a father.

75
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,439
Mao Ge didn't have to kill anyone.

76
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:54,000
I didn't have to get dragged into this.

77
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,319
All these years, I helped Mao Ge

78
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,439
beat so many charges.

79
00:03:57,599 --> 00:03:58,159
I...

80
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,680
I never did him wrong.

81
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,159
I...

82
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,879
I did my best, Huang Qiuping.

83
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,400
But I had no choice.

84
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:06,000
He...

85
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:07,560
He...

86
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,280
I was afraid of being found out.

87
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:11,199
I had no choice but to...

88
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,479
chop him up,

89
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,039
toss him into the fish grinder,

90
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,879
and dump him into the sea.

91
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:20,759
I...

92
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:21,519
I...

93
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,160
A burial at sea.

94
00:04:22,319 --> 00:04:23,000
No.

95
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,360
That's good.

96
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,360
So you...

97
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,439
Min Ge.

98
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:40,439
That gigolo with Huang Qiuping just came out.

99
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:54,319
Keep watch from the car.

100
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,920
I'll head upstairs and check.

101
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,480
Huang Qiuping.

102
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,240
Huang Qiuping, I was wrong.

103
00:05:18,319 --> 00:05:19,319
What are you doing?

104
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,360
Let's go together.

105
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,600
Min Ge, where are we going now?

106
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:39,079
I'm asking you. Where to?

107
00:05:39,199 --> 00:05:40,040
Where's the money?

108
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:45,319
Mao Ge stashed the money

109
00:05:45,319 --> 00:05:46,680
in a warehouse by the sea.

110
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:49,360
The key's in my auto shop's safe.

111
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:51,759
Let's go.

112
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,240
Auto repair shop.

113
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:03,639
Sir.

114
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:05,160
Luo Xiao and Huang Qiuping were forced

115
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,560
into a grey van by some guy.

116
00:06:06,879 --> 00:06:08,839
The plate ends in 3397.

117
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,040
The guy's got a knife.

118
00:06:10,199 --> 00:06:11,120
The van's got tinted windows.

119
00:06:11,319 --> 00:06:12,319
I can't tell how many are inside.

120
00:06:13,519 --> 00:06:14,600
Okay, okay, keep your distance.

121
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,000
Stay back, don't tip them off.

122
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,839
We're heading over right now.

123
00:06:17,199 --> 00:06:17,800
Got it.

124
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:20,759
Zhang Da.

125
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:21,879
The test results are in.

126
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:22,959
It's a human fingernail.

127
00:06:24,319 --> 00:06:25,560
Jin Qiang, Xiao Ru.

128
00:06:26,079 --> 00:06:27,079
Take them back to the station first.

129
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:28,560
Investigate everyone involved thoroughly.

130
00:06:28,639 --> 00:06:29,480
Don't leave any loose ends.

131
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,959
Precinct officers, secure the scene.

132
00:06:31,079 --> 00:06:32,360
Forensics, do a full inspection.

133
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:33,519
Everyone else, come with me.

134
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,319
Yes, sir.

135
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,120
Ma Dui.

136
00:06:35,399 --> 00:06:36,279
Send cars for backup.

137
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,399
Got it.

138
00:06:50,439 --> 00:06:51,160
Ah Min.

139
00:06:52,839 --> 00:06:54,560
He's been using me all along.

140
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,519
This is all a misunderstanding between us.

141
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:01,279
If it weren't for Luo Xiao,

142
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,160
the two of us

143
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,959
wouldn't have any beef at all.

144
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,680
Once you grab the money,

145
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:07,879
just get out of here fast.

146
00:07:08,199 --> 00:07:09,399
I'll keep an eye on Luo Xiao for you.

147
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,480
You haven't killed anyone yet.

148
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,160
Run far away.

149
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,600
The cops won't chase you that hard.

150
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:19,480
Yap, yap, yap.

151
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,680
Are you done yet?

152
00:07:20,959 --> 00:07:22,240
Shut your mouth.

153
00:07:26,439 --> 00:07:27,439
What are you doing?

154
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,839
Bro, it's really not my fault.

155
00:07:28,839 --> 00:07:30,160
Can you drive?

156
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,439
That car up ahead,

157
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:32,959
tell him to move it.

158
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,519
Drive, drive, drive!

159
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:10,759
Look at the state of him.

160
00:08:11,759 --> 00:08:13,680
You think he could kill Mao Ge?

161
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,120
Huang Qiuping, do you buy that?

162
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,240
Where's the stuff?

163
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,039
I'll stab you.

164
00:09:36,679 --> 00:09:37,519
And yours.

165
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,320
What are you stalling for?

166
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:53,039
Stop stalling.

167
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:54,600
You hear me?

168
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,519
Are you playing me?

169
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,639
Get over here.

170
00:10:15,279 --> 00:10:15,960
Min Shengquan!

171
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:16,639
Back off!

172
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,559
Drop the knife.

173
00:10:17,559 --> 00:10:18,279
Back off!

174
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:19,480
Or I'll kill him.

175
00:10:19,559 --> 00:10:20,559
Nobody has to die.

176
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:21,759
Stay calm.

177
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,679
Back off.

178
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:23,320
Okay.

179
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:24,240
You back off too.

180
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,240
Drop the knife.

181
00:10:28,279 --> 00:10:30,039
You have to let me walk today.

182
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:31,840
Or get ready to collect a body.

183
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,279
Drop the knife.

184
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:35,080
You have to let me go.

185
00:10:41,879 --> 00:10:42,559
Don't move!

186
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,200
You okay?

187
00:10:48,279 --> 00:10:49,200
Your ear's bleeding.

188
00:10:49,639 --> 00:10:50,639
I'll call you an ambulance.

189
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,120
Take him back.

190
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,279
Let go of me!

191
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:58,240
How's it going with Luo Xiao?

192
00:10:58,399 --> 00:10:59,120
He's already inside.

193
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,679
His wound's treated. It's not serious.

194
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:01,759
Ready for interrogation.

195
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:03,360
Sir, let Ma Dui and me handle it.

196
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,559
It's inappropriate given your background.

197
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:07,559
At the time, I was at Fengmao.

198
00:11:08,639 --> 00:11:09,799
helping handle

199
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:12,320
Huang Qiuping's marital asset division.

200
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,519
After what happened to Chen Yongjiang,

201
00:11:15,799 --> 00:11:17,440
the whole Fengmao fell into chaos.

202
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:20,080
Everyone wanted to cash in.

203
00:11:20,879 --> 00:11:22,360
Including Min Shengquan.

204
00:11:23,159 --> 00:11:25,080
I've said it many times already.

205
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:26,799
I didn't kill him.

206
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:29,080
It was Luo Xiao. He's the mastermind.

207
00:11:29,399 --> 00:11:32,360
He conspired with Huang Qiuping a long time ago to swallow up

208
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:34,200
Fengmao's money.

209
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,799
Enough. What are you mumbling about?

210
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:37,240
Where do you think you are?

211
00:11:37,759 --> 00:11:38,720
The police station.

212
00:11:39,759 --> 00:11:41,519
You think you'd be sitting here if we didn't have evidence?

213
00:11:42,679 --> 00:11:43,519
No.

214
00:11:43,919 --> 00:11:45,360
I really didn't kill him.

215
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:47,000
If you don't believe me, ask Huang Qiuping.

216
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:49,000
Huang Qiuping can prove I'm telling the truth.

217
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,159
Huang Qiuping is dead.

218
00:11:51,919 --> 00:11:53,039
He kept dragging out the payment.

219
00:11:53,799 --> 00:11:55,519
Huang Qiuping was extremely unhappy.

220
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:59,279
So the two started turning on each other.

221
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,000
And in the end,

222
00:12:01,799 --> 00:12:03,080
they dragged me into it.

223
00:12:03,559 --> 00:12:04,919
Then why did he end up

224
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:07,200
at your auto repair shop?

225
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,840
He said he wanted a sum of money.

226
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,840
A sum of money to skip town.

227
00:12:11,559 --> 00:12:12,759
He was out for blood.

228
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,679
He couldn't just let me walk, right?

229
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:17,720
You're lying to me.

230
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:21,480
You're lying, aren't you? Aren't you?

231
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:22,320
Watch your attitude.

232
00:12:22,399 --> 00:12:23,600
What attitude?

233
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,960
No, it's impossible.

234
00:12:29,559 --> 00:12:30,879
I didn't mean to, I...

235
00:12:31,159 --> 00:12:31,840
I...

236
00:12:32,879 --> 00:12:35,039
Tell us everything you know.

237
00:12:35,639 --> 00:12:37,840
Why did you blow up Zhang Yuanshan's house?

238
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,600
Luo Xiao told me to.

239
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,039
Your auto repair shop

240
00:12:46,039 --> 00:12:47,559
was acquired from Zhang Yuanshan.

241
00:12:47,799 --> 00:12:49,399
Then Zhang Yuanshan came to cause trouble for you.

242
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:51,399
And then Min Shengquan blew up his house.

243
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:53,000
Two completely unrelated people,

244
00:12:53,159 --> 00:12:54,120
both connected to you.

245
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:58,720
I don't know.

246
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,080
I really have no idea.

247
00:13:01,759 --> 00:13:03,120
He said Mao Ge was hiding there.

248
00:13:04,519 --> 00:13:05,240
So...

249
00:13:05,879 --> 00:13:06,679
What do you mean?

250
00:13:07,279 --> 00:13:08,559
Explain the whole story clearly.

251
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,600
Every word he confesses now

252
00:13:12,679 --> 00:13:14,840
could earn him a reduced sentence.

253
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:15,919
Do you think

254
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:18,519
he'll cover for you, or come clean for leniency?

255
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:26,279
Min Shengquan, get one thing straight.

256
00:13:26,919 --> 00:13:28,240
Only we can help you now.

257
00:13:28,399 --> 00:13:30,360
This is your last chance. Understand?

258
00:13:43,159 --> 00:13:43,879
Okay.

259
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,080
I'll talk.

260
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,879
The day of Mao Ge's incident,

261
00:13:55,559 --> 00:13:56,879
Min Shengquan claims

262
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:00,679
Luo Xiao was the one who sent him off.
